# UI: shadcn/ui + TenantShield theme

## Component strategy (order)

1. **Reuse** primitives under `@/components/ui` (see `components.json`).
2. **If missing** from the shadcn registry: `pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add <component>`.
3. **One-off UI**: implement inline in the page/feature with React + Tailwind + **theme tokens**. Do not add shared components for tiny markup.

Extract a component only when reused heavily or state grows.

## `app/globals.css` is the single source of truth

- **No** ad-hoc hex/HSL or raw palette utilities (`bg-zinc-900`, `text-amber-300`) for product UI.
- **Do** use tokens exposed via `@theme inline` and `:root` / `.dark`.

### Tenant-facing “cream” layer (ratings, profile rows, warm marketing)

Use these for warm pages and cards on cream backgrounds:

- `bg-cream-page` — page canvas
- `bg-cream-surface`, `bg-cream-surface-soft`, `bg-cream-surface-deep` — cards / fills
- `border-cream-border` — borders on cream UI
- `text-ink-warm`, `text-ink-warm-muted` — body copy on cream
- `bg-surface-strong`, `hover:bg-surface-strong-hover`, `text-white` — **primary dark CTAs** on cream (matches selected filter chips, high contrast)

### shadcn / forms layer (auth, inputs, default app chrome)

Still use standard semantic tokens:

- Surfaces: `bg-background`, `bg-popover`, `bg-card`, `text-foreground`, `text-card-foreground`, `border-border`, `bg-accent`
- Actions: `bg-primary`, `text-primary-foreground`, `bg-secondary`, `text-secondary-foreground`
- Feedback: `text-destructive`, `border-destructive`, `text-warning`, `bg-warning`
- Focus: `ring-ring`, `border-input`

Light/dark: extend **only** in `globals.css` (`:root` / `.dark` + `@theme inline` when adding a new `--color-*`). Do not add parallel color systems in TS or random CSS files.

## Examples

```tsx
// ✅ Cream page + dark CTA (ratings, similar flows)
<Button className="bg-surface-strong text-white hover:bg-surface-strong-hover">Give a rating</Button>
<section className="rounded-2xl border border-cream-border bg-cream-surface/40 p-4">…</section>

// ✅ Auth / forms (shadcn + defaults)
<Input className="border-border bg-popover" />
<Button variant="default">Save</Button>

// ❌ Avoid
<div className="bg-[#f5f0e8] text-[#1a1a1a]" />
```

Match existing patterns: Radix + `cn()` + `class-variance-authority` in `@/components/ui`.
